## Medical Disclaimer

MediScan is an educational and research-based AI medical analysis project. The predictions and results generated by this software are not intended to replace professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.

Users should always consult qualified healthcare professionals before making any medical decisions based on the outputs of this application.

The developers of MediScan are not responsible for any medical decisions, diagnoses, treatments, or outcomes resulting from the use of this software.

