## Third-Party Libraries and Models

This project uses open-source libraries and frameworks including:

* Python
* Flask
* TensorFlow / Keras
* Scikit-learn
* Hugging Face Transformers
* PyTorch
* NumPy
* Pandas
* OpenCV

Some pre-trained models, datasets, or weights may have their own licenses and usage restrictions. Users are responsible for checking the licenses of any third-party datasets, model weights, or external assets included in the project.
